 
== Interface Overview

T-MSIS collects Medicaid and CHIP data from U.S. states, territories, and the District of
Columbia into the largest national resource of beneficiary information. This data supports
research, policy, and CMS program oversight.
The data is extracted from Hawaii’s HPMMIS and sent to CMS. AHCCCS provides raw
extracts without filtering, editing, or quality checks.

